<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <title>Commande terminée - Musée du Louvre</title>

    {# On charge le CSS de bootstrap depuis le site directement #}
    <!-- Latest compiled and minified CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-BVYiiSIFeK1dGmJRAkycuHAHRg32OmUcww7on3RYdg4Va+PmSTsz/K68vbdEjh4u" crossorigin="anonymous">

    <!-- Optional theme -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap-theme.min.css" integrity="sha384-rHyoN1iRsVXV4nD0JutlnGaslCJuC7uwjduW9SVrLvRYooPp2bWYgmgJQIXwl/Sp" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/3.3.5/css/bootstrap.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <title>Merci de votre commande</title>
</head>
<body>
<div class="row">
    <h2><img src="{{ url }}" alt="logo Musee du louvre" /> Voici le récapitulatif de votre commande</h2>
    <table class="table table-striped table-hover ">
        <thead>
        <tr>
            <th> Numéro de votre Commande :</th>
        </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
        <tr class="info">
            <td>{{ recapCde.codeReserv }}</td>
        </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
</div>
<div class="row">
    <table class="table table-striped table-hover ">
        <thead>
        <tr>
            <th> Date de votre visite :</th>
        </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
        <tr class="info">
            <td>{{ recapCde.dateVisite|localizeddate('full', 'none') }}</td>
        </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
</div>
<div class="row">
    <table class="table table-striped table-hover ">
        <thead>
        <tr>
            <th> votre E-mail :</th>
        </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
        <tr class="info">
            <td>{{ recapCde.email }}</td>
        </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
</div>
<div class="row">
    <table class="table table-striped table-hover ">
        <thead>
        <tr>
            <th colspan="4"> Informations sur vos billets : {{ recapCde.nbBillet }} billet(s)</th>
        </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody id="table-body">
        {% for recapbillet in recapBillets %}
            <tr>

                <td class="text-left">{{ recapbillet.nom }} {{ recapbillet.prenom }}</td>
                <td class="text-left">{{ recapbillet.dateNaissance|date('d/m/Y') }}</td>
                <td class="text-right"> {{ recapbillet.montant }} € TTC</td>
            </tr>
        {% endfor %}
        </tbody>
        <tbody>
        <tr class="info">
            <th colspan="2" class="text-left">Total de votre commande</th>
            <th class="text-right" id="total-price"> {{ recapCde.montantTotal }} € TTC</td>
        </tr>
        </tbody>
    </table>
        <p>Merci de présenter ce document à la caisse, ainsi que toutes pièces justificatives nécessaires pour les tarifs réduits.</p>
</div>
</body>

</html>
